MOST IMPORTANT FEATURES
https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/features/

1. Swagger - No need for POSTMAN for testing, call and test your API
directly from the browser with documentation

2. Supports Concurrency and async / await
https://fastapi.tiangolo.com/async/#in-a-hurry



----- commands -------------
for running api - uvicorn 'filename -py without .py': 'fastAPI object' --reload
example uvicorn main:app --reload